TWA announces
two new elite levels of
FFB® Join the TWA Frequent Flight Bonus
Program. You'll fly in comfort, with
membership. up to 50% more legroom than any
other major U.S. airline. Every mile
you fly on TWA can count toward
free travel worldwide. And the miles
you earn have no expiration date.
What's more, when you fly just
20,000 actual miles on TWA or
TW Express® (or four transatlantic
segments) within 12 months, you'll
move up one level to the TWA
Gold Ambassador® card. It entitles
you to upgrades on many fares and
extra bonus miles: At 40,000
actua miles on TWA or TW Express
(or eight transatlantic segments)
within 12 months, you'll qualify for
the ultimate privilege — the FFB
Royal Ambassador® card, with an
even more generous upgrade policy
and additional bonus miles:
To enroll in the FFB Program, call
TWA toll-free at (800) 221-2000 in
the United States. Outside the U.S.,
call your local TWA office.
*Upgrades are subject to availability.
Purchase of a qualifying ticket is required.
